\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1854332 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9056586\charrsid10431346 So you lived there from - if you were born in -
